ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0858e08744cc46beb8a6956906075b1cf59f18ae","tid":815992,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9947563aa2aee0d7e5a44c313479382dafeba1e2","tid":815992,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb6ab68882f3a547c986f43538542d5b1789eaf","tid":815992,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb620640367200e66910b20175902a6076ba417d","tid":815992,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T03:42:12.000Z","msg":"支持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T06:21:27.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707360e752eb9d195d669cdac21b8a0865ac30cc","tid":815992,"uid":38775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d287ed29899a52cc5b2278e2635fbaeae51fdbcb","tid":815992,"uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"小弟其他文章: <br />\n耶教史（上）由多神教演變成一神教<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/796868/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/796868/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n漢傳佛教的陰暗面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/799364/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/799364/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n印度教神話(一)--任意妄為的鬼父梵天(四面佛原型)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/800994/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/800994/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[學術討論] 佛經所載真的是佛陀所說?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/801983/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/801983/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n印度教神話(二) 破壞神濕婆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/807236/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/807236/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"以前讀書聽過耶教本身係多神宗教<br />\n不過就話傳去歐洲個陣為左強化皇權先變一神<br />\n原來係中東已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打有無聽過耶穌去印度修行呢個傳說？<br />\n如果有會唔會係下半部講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6372d9f86c86e9aabf32941d8d8ee35f8918fd6d","tid":815992,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"707360e752eb9d195d669cdac21b8a0865ac30cc","tid":815992,"uid":38775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d287ed29899a52cc5b2278e2635fbaeae51fdbcb","tid":815992,"uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T12:37:14.000Z","msg":"小弟其他文章: <br />\n耶教史（上）由多神教演變成一神教<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/796868/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/796868/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n漢傳佛教的陰暗面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/799364/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/799364/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n印度教神話(一)--任意妄為的鬼父梵天(四面佛原型)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/800994/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/800994/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[學術討論] 佛經所載真的是佛陀所說?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/801983/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/801983/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n印度教神話(二) 破壞神濕婆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/807236/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/807236/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"以前讀書聽過耶教本身係多神宗教<br />\n不過就話傳去歐洲個陣為左強化皇權先變一神<br />\n原來係中東已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打有無聽過耶穌去印度修行呢個傳說？<br />\n如果有會唔會係下半部講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"而家講少少, 得閒先寫文詳細講<br />\n歷史上的耶穌係難以還原, 因為正史對佢記載太少<br />\n學者最多只係由聖經既眾多福音中對照, 再按一啲「原則」去估佢係咩人<br />\n福音, 即使最早個部都係耶穌死左十幾年先出黎, 仲要有好多後人編輯, 唔同福音又唔代表唔同派別(早期基督教分好多派別, 主張唔係咁統一)<br />\n所以學界無共識耶穌係咩人,情況同佛陀好似, 就係現代其實無人實際肯定佢講過咩<br />\n<br />\n有趣既係, 其中一派學者估計(特別係第三波), 耶穌未必主張過博愛, 反而係好猶太主義, 賤視非猶太人, 好排外, 佢係因叛亂罪而被殺, 而釘十字架個陣, 佢隔離個兩個唔係賊, 而係都係搞叛亂, 革命既人,  係翻譯出錯先以為係小偷<br />\n<br />\n博愛個啲係保羅講<br />\n咩上天堂落地獄都未必係早期基督教既主張, 係後世加上去同其他宗教競爭而黎<br />\n<br />\n當然其他派別神學家唔係咁睇, 佢地信博愛真係出自基督啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2c6281d1d5f36583d73539c5d45dc124bca34f","tid":815992,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}